<servinfosub id = "AENAP70BA804004002">
<title>
Diagnosis Procedure
</title>
<ptxt>
When “CAN Communication Bus Off” is detected in any control modules, or when it is not possible to communicate with all control modules / sensor with CAN using SUZUKI scan tool, check the following procedure.
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Connect oscilloscope or SUZUKI scan tool to DLC when ignition is “OFF”.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using oscilloscope or oscilloscope function of SUZUKI scan tool, observe waveform in the following condition when ignition is “ON”.
</ptxt>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "3" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.285in"/>
