</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
In case of CAN High signal wire is shorted to ground circuit
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Both of CAN High signal and CAN Low signal are fixed to GND level (0 V)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<emph>
In case of CAN Low signal wire is shorted to ground circuit
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Reference level of both CAN High signal and CAN Low signal is GND level (0 V) and CAN High signal waveform oscillates irregularly.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
CAN High signal: Between 0 V and 3 V
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CAN Low signal: Fixed to 0 V
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
