<servinfosub id = "AENAP70BA804004024">
<title>
Judgment of Communication Bus Check 
</title>
<ptxt>
When performing “Communication Bus Check” using SUZUKI scan tool, refer to the following table for judgment.
</ptxt>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.542in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "5.677in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Judgment
